Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,REVIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, please,\Nlet me go and make the arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to come with you, Chief,\Nif that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, but remember this is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to take every precaution\Nwhen you approach him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't allow him to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, if Higuchi tries anything\Nor makes any sudden moves…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Understood. I will shoot\Nto stop him, not to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa, do you have a helmet\Nor something to hide your face with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Then cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. You can count on me, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[quick footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Higuchi, put your hands\Nabove your head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and get out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] We've apprehended him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi, I want you to put a headset on him\Nas planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Higuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you able to kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use whatever means necessary\Nto get it out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've got a special notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I write someone's name in it\Nwhile thinking of their face,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that person dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A notebook…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Yeah, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in one of the compartments\Nof Higuchi's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He has written a lot of names in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but there doesn't seem to be\Nanything else unusual about it. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] What is it, Mr. Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic; remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not really armed\Nto defend yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… oh right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Chief, hang in there.\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi, can't you see that thing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I think you must be getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] That… that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that only people\Nwho have touched the notebook can…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can see this… this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Please bring the notebook\Nover to the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Uh… o-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you planning to do,\NLight Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you take hold of that notebook again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all the memories of the Death Note\Nand what you did when it was yours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,will return at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Here it is, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is… a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They really… do… exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light Yagami…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how Kira killed.\NNo, the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[L's thoughts echoing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, come on, let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] The Second Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Two books!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There have to be two notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[echoing voices and sounds]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Are you okay, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose seeing that monster\Nwould surprise anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuzaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I wanna check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try comparing the names\Nwritten in this notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with the names of the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby forfeit\Nownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that means ownership\Nhas transferred back to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Yes, I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Next, pass it on to Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Very well. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that notebook's ownership\Nhas transferred from you to Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ryuk, take the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and drop it on the ground,\Nso it's in the human world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the ownership goes back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, hang on!\NIt’s just gone around in a circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe at first glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but there will be a time\Nwhen I'll benefit from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as for this notebook,\Nthe one I first received,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna give it back to you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you hand it over to Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, I want you to give the notebook\Nto someone with status
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,who lusts for power and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll end up using the notebook\Nto satisfy that urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guarantee that Misa will be\Nreleased from her confinement soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I'm wrong, and it looks like\Nshe won’t be released for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound fair to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami, just what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this is all to save Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to trust me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it means that Misa will be saved,\NI'll do as you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] After this, I'll go and demand\Nto be confined like Misa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them put me\Nunder 24-hour surveillance as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm locked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll relinquish ownership of the notebook\Nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll mean I'll lose\Nall my memories of the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,During this time the killings of criminals\Nwill start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA RETURNS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki will be put in a position\Nwhere he has to release us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And, after I've lost all my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,chances are\NI'll wanna help catch Kira myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then you'll try and catch the guy\Nwho Rem gives the notebook to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and steal it before L gets to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that's done,\NI'll kill the new owner of the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still one problem remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] If you don't have full ownership,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your memories will only return for as long\Nas you're in contact with the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you let go of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your memories will disappear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That means I've gotta kill Higuchi\Nwithout letting go of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I manage to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ownership will transfer back to me\Nand my memories won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to pull this four times\Nin less than a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing this watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami,\Nplease take Higuchi to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Uh, right. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,KYOSUKE HIGUCHI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] You know, about this notebook…\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I wonder what we would find\Nif we put it through forensic analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] That doesn't sound like you,\NLight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We both know this thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps echoing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This has gotta be\Nthe longest 40 seconds of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, Higuchi is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hey, Higuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Dad, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose him!\NIf Higuchi dies on us now--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The… but… [sighs]\NThere's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yes. He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're next,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] "How to use it."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, "The human whose name\Nis written in this notebook…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"This note will not take effect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,unless the writer has the person's face\Nin their mind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when writing his or her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, people sharing the same name\Nwill not be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light typing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] If the cause of death is written\N40 seconds of writing the person’s name,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is not specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the person will simply die\Nof a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After writing the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,details of the death should be written\Nin the next six minutes and 40 seconds."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As well, the back cover has some more\Ninstructions on how to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two more rules.\NOne of them is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you make this note unusable\Nby tearing it up or burning it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all the humans\Nwho have touched the note till then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-will die."\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really true, Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Aizawa] Yeah, that’s what it says.\N-[Light] That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] No way! That sucks!\N-[Light] With a rule like that in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] Why didn't you tell me\Nbefore I touched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-... the notebook's safety is guaranteed.\N[Aizawa] How was I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Which means my memories\Nof it will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Rem, there's no way\Nthe old man back home
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,will get mad at us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if we write fake rules in here, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] No. There are no rules\Nagainst doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then, Light, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you owe me an apple for this.\N[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, maybe I shouldn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,let my curiosity about seeing a Shinigami\Nget the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but then you would be\Nthe only one in the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,who didn't know what we were dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be on the same page\Nas everyone else on the Task Force, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then… [sighs] there's this last rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,According to these instructions\Nin the back of the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the person using the note
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,fails to consecutively write\Nnames of people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to be killed\Nwithin thirteen days of each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,then the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda gasps] Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then it means Light and Misa-Misa\Nare completely clear, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Yeah, now that you mention it,\Nthat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Light and Misa were detained\Nfor more than 50 days
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and are still under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If either of them had been Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way\Nthey would still be alive by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that’s great news, isn't it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your name, isn't it?\NThe white thing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, isn't it a bit rude to go around\Ncalling someone a "white thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] There's more than one notebook\Nin the human world, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be and there may not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are other notebooks either here\Nor in your world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,would they all have the same rules\Nas this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get Rem\Nto admit these rules are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Yes, they are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many notebooks\Nin the Shinigami Realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but they all have the same rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the rules\Nfor when humans obtain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Misa Amane and Light have both\Nbeen cleared of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They shouldn’t be under surveillance\Nany longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] That's right,\Nit's crystal clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Please, except my apologies\Nfor all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda and Aizawa sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We still can’t say we’ve solved the case\Nuntil we’ve figured out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if I kept investigating with you,\Nwithout the handcuffs on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] And just like that,\NMisa and I are proven innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A notebook of death filled with rules\Nwritten by a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no choice but to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He just lost his edge\Nthanks to the fake rules I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Ryuzaki:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what the world,\Nthe god of that world creates the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, you've already been defeated\Nby the rules I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And as punishment\Nfor defying the god of the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to text me every day, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] After all this time,\Nwe're saying goodbye to Misa-Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Matsuda!\NLet's leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Goodbye Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Good,\Nthere are surveillance cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but they won't be able to pick out\Nmy face or mouth at this angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, I'm gonna tell you\Nabout a special place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to go there\Nand dig something up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have to make sure\Nthat no one is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Your memory must have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Light, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everything that happened\Nwhen I had this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You buried this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could come here\Nand regain my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,FOR MISA, LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's voice] "Dear Misa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time you read this letter,\Nyou should've remembered everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a letter from Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Do you remember\Nmy friend at To-Oh University?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He went by the name "Hideki Ryuga."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to write his real name\Nin the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then burn this letter right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a number of pages from the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and rebury it where you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time that we see each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,casually touch me\Nwith a piece of the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I will love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-for the rest of my life.\N-[Misa] …for the rest of my life! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all part of Light's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to get this notebook,\Nregain all my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then kill Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One of Light's biggest obstacles\Nwill be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be helpful to him at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Light, it's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t remember his name anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was seeing dozens-- no,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,no, no hundreds of names and lifespans\Nevery day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I can't remember it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally return to the human world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Oh, it's been so long!\NOh, I'm so glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-How are you doing?\N-Sorry, uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a guy, I get a little shy,\Nsome… times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Oh yeah, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Light told me to bring one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Oh yeah. Human apples are--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the word-- juicy, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're great, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[mumbles] Why don't you try this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk gulps]\NAn apple from the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh… Ew, it doesn't look very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, one bite won't kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, before I forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to make the eye deal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa biting apple]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Peh! Peh! It's sand! Bleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You already made the same deal with Rem\Nonce before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you really want me\Nto cut your lifespan in half,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for the second time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I know, but what choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I've forgotten a name\Nthat I absolutely have to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Light will be so mad at me\Nif I let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, well it's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Hey, it's Misa-Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're stuck in here,\Nwe can't turn our cellphones on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so she has to come all the way out here\Njust to hang out with Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, would you hurry up and go see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know,\Nyou should never keep a woman waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he attached to Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Misa's lifespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been halved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Did she make the eye deal with Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember Hideki Ryuga's real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried, but I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did the eye deal with Ryuk,\Nso I can try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everything's going according to plan…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that,\Nthen your lifespan will--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm… no, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be of use to you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, all I want is
